data.description: **BACK ON MARKET** Previous buyer did not qualify for loan, his LOSS and your WIN!! You found it- POOL HOME ALERT! Nestled in the heart of Murrieta, this stunning 4-berdroom / 2.5-bathroom residence at 38464 Coralino Drive offers the perfect blend of modern luxury, family-friendly features, and a prime location for military families. Immerse yourself in a spacious haven that not only provides comfort but also caters to the unique needs of those seeking a safe and convenient lifestyle. Step into a world of comfort with generously sized living areas, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining guests. The open floor plan creates an inviting atmosphere, while large windows bathe the interiors in natural light. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the modern kitchen, equipped with top-of-the-line appliances and ample counter space. Whether you're a culinary enthusiast or a busy family, this kitchen is designed to meet your needs. The adjoining family dining area is ideal for cozy meals with loved ones. Escape to your private oasis in the expansive backyard, featuring lush greenery and plenty of space for outdoor activities. It's a perfect playground for kids and a serene spot for adults to unwind. Imagine summer barbecues, garden parties, and creating cherished memories under the California sun. For families with school-age children, this home is located in close proximity to award-winning schools, ensuring an excellent education for the next generation. Convenience meets quality in this family-oriented neighborhood. Enjoy the convenience of being minutes away from the Promenade Mall, local parks, and a variety of amenities. This location offers the perfect balance of tranquility and accessibility. Proximity to military bases and a welcoming community make this property an ideal residence for our heroes. Don't miss the opportunity to call 38464 Coralino Drive home. Schedule your private tour now and discover the perfect blend of elegance, functionality, and family-friendly living. Your dream home awaits!
